    |=  name=input-name
    ^-  (unit preinput)
    =/  res  (~(get of tree) /input/[name])
    ?~  res  ~
    ?.  ?=(%input -.u.res)  ~
    `preinput.u.res
  ::    +get-seed: retrieve a seed by name
