    |=  name=seed-name
    ^-  (unit preseed)
    =/  res  (~(get of tree) /seed/[name])
    ?~  res  ~
    ?.  ?=(%seed -.u.res)  ~
    `preseed.u.res
  ::    +add-draft: add a new draft
